title: Opie & Jim Norton JUL 27 2015 Mon.mp3
description:
THANKS TO @SternGeek FOR THE FILE

Opie & Jim Norton JUL 27 2015 Mon (03:25:33)

On today's show: Vic Henley, Esther Ku, DL Hughley, Greg Louganis, Nathaniel Rateliff & The Night Sweats.

* Hulk Hogan & the Brooke Hogan poem.
* Vic Henley Talking Nantucket, co-op boards, and NYC outdoor space, Endurance,         
  Shackleton and the Antarctic. 
* Jim Channels Larry Flynt.
* Esther Ku  Wearing a half-shirt.
* DL Hughley calls in talking about a run-in back in 2009 with Bill Cosby.
* Greg louganis discussing his HBO documentary "Back On Board" 
* Nathaniel Rateliff & The Night Sweats Perform & chat
